data.title: Beach hotels and coastal getaways
data.meta_description: Looking for a luxurious hotel next to a beach with golden sand, a villa above the dark blue of the Mediterranean or a small bed & breakfast in the hills overlooking the ocean …
data.text:
A curated selection of the best and most beautiful beach hotels and holiday homes with ocean view.

Are you looking for a luxurious hotel on a beautiful beach with golden sand, a villa above the bright blue sea or a small bed & breakfast on a rugged cliff overlooking the ocean? Longing for a few relaxing days on the beach to finally feel the warm sun on your skin again? Discover our selection of the best charming beach hotels and seaside accommodations and let yourself be enchanted. From family-run romantic B&Bs near the ocean to luxury hotels on the beach, our portfolio offers a wide variety of lodgings on some of the most beautiful coasts. Our list ranges from contemporary and stylish places to stay in trendy coastal regions all the way to coastal getaways filled with history in off-the-beaten-track locations. But they all have one thing in common: they have been personally selected by us for their excellence, authenticity and beauty so that you don't have to worry about anything and can simply enjoy your dream vacation by the coast.
